<br>
If you are saying how to use your druid to PL your cleric- maybe BW?  Use the druid to snare and pull. Damage shield the cleric and let him/her nuke the undead and tank the last bit.  See if Atone works (dunno if it will). Have the druid quad some stuff, then atone and finish with the cleric?<br>
<br>
Shaiel<br>
